1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

CVSS v4 9.4
ATTENTION: Exploitable remotely/low attack complexity
Vendor: Siemens
Equipment: SCALANCE W700
Vulnerability: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements in Output Used by a Downstream Component ('Injection')

2. RISK EVALUATION
Successful exploitation of this vulnerability could allow an authenticated remote attacker with administrative privileges to inject code or spawn a system root shell.
